{"timestamp":1774434285946,"source_app":"agentic-harness","session_id":"7207faa8-a586-4139-931c-ecdc841081e8","hook_event_type":"PreToolUse","tool_name":"Write","tool_use_id":"toolu_01Mt64GqokWdpQbKGuwe93YG","payload":{"session_id":"7207faa8-a586-4139-931c-ecdc841081e8","transcript_path":"/Users/auto/.claude/projects/-Users-auto-agentic-harness-apps-mas-trees-cc24365d/7207faa8-a586-4139-931c-ecdc841081e8.jsonl","cwd":"/Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/cc24365d","permission_mode":"bypassPermissions","hook_event_name":"PreToolUse","tool_name":"Write","tool_input":{"file_path":"/Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/cc24365d/specs/issue-cc24365d-adw-07232995-sdlc_planner-remove-footer-from-plans-page.md","content":"# Plan: Remove footer from plans page\n\n## Task Description\nRemove the `<footer>` element from the plans variant merch card render layout. The footer currently contains a secure transaction label and a `<slot name=\"footer\">` (used for CTAs/buy buttons). The footer element should be removed from the plans page layout while preserving CTA rendering by moving `<slot name=\"footer\">` into the `.body` div. Dead CSS targeting `<footer>` in the plans variant should also be cleaned up.\n\n## Relevant Files\n\n- `web-components/src/variants/plans.js` \u2014 Contains `renderLayout()` which renders `${this.secureLabelFooter}`, and `variantStyle` CSS with footer-specific rules. Primary file to edit.\n- `web-components/src/variants/variant-layout.js` \u2014 Defines the shared `secureLabelFooter` getter. Read-only \u2014 do not modify (shared by other variants).\n- `web-components/src/variants/plans.css.js` \u2014 Contains global CSS for plans variant. Has `[slot=\"footer\"]` styles that remain valid and should not be removed.\n\n## Step by Step Tasks\n\n### 1. Remove `secureLabelFooter` from `renderLayout()` in `plans.js`\n- In `renderLayout()` (line ~329), remove `${this.secureLabelFooter}` from the template literal\n- Add `<slot name=\"footer\"></slot>` at the bottom of the `.body` div, after `<slot name=\"badge\"></slot>`, so CTAs continue to render\n\n### 2. Remove dead footer CSS from `variantStyle` in `plans.js`\n- Remove the `:host([variant^='plans']) footer { ... }` rule (padding styles)\n- Remove the `:host([variant^='plans']) footer ::slotted([slot='addon']) { ... }` rule\n- Remove the `:host([variant='plans']) .wide-footer #stock-checkbox { ... }` rule (wide-footer class is only added to the now-removed footer element)\n\n### 3. Validate no breakage in `adjustSlotPlacement`\n- The `adjustSlotPlacement` method queries `shadowRoot.querySelector('footer')` \u2014 with footer removed it returns `null` and the `footer?.classList` optional chains are safe no-ops\n- No changes needed; verify the method handles null footer gracefully (it does via optional chaining)\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- The plans merch card renders without a `<footer>` element in its shadow DOM\n- CTAs (slot=\"footer\" content) still render inside the `.body` div\n- The secure transaction label is no longer shown on plans cards\n- No layout breakage \u2014 body padding and card structure intact\n- No unused CSS rules targeting `<footer>` remain in `plans.js` variantStyle\n- Other variants (product, catalog, segment, etc.) are unaffected\n\n## Validation Commands\n- `node --check web-components/src/variants/plans.js`\n"},"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Mt64GqokWdpQbKGuwe93YG"}}
